summary: This collection of documents pertains to a payment issue involving Edvard G. Tichborn. It includes a memorandum discussing a delayed payment and a telegram from Tichborn (under the alias Henry Lopez) inquiring about the status of the payment from Ashmead, Hanniferd & Associates.
title: Payment to Edvard G. Tichborn
sender: Evalena S. Vidal, Political Action Division and Henry Lopez (Edvard G. Tichborn)
